{"id":373,"parent_id":351,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":373,"title":"1 Chronicles 22","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Chr.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 22"],[".studySummary",["i","David prepares gold, silver, brass, iron, stone, and cedar wood for the temple—He charges Solomon to do the work of building it."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.1","order":"02.14.022.28799"},["b","1"],"Then David said, This",["i","is"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"house"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God, and this",["i","is"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"altar"],"of the burnt offering for Israel."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.2","order":"02.14.022.28800"},["b","2"],"And David commanded to gather together the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"strangers"],"that",["i","were"],"in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"land of Israel"],"; and he set masons to hew wrought stones to build the house of God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.3","order":"02.14.022.28801"},["b","3"],"And David prepared iron in abundance for the nails for the doors of the gates, and for the joinings; and brass in abundance without weight;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.4","order":"02.14.022.28802"},["b","4"],"Also cedar trees in abundance: for the Zidonians and they of Tyre brought much",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"cedar"],"wood to David."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.5","order":"02.14.022.28803"},["b","5"],"And David said, Solomon my son",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"young"],"and tender, and the house",["i","that is"],"to be builded for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","must be"],"exceeding magnifical, of fame and of glory throughout all countries: I will",["i","therefore"],"now make preparation for it. So David prepared abundantly before his death."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.6","order":"02.14.022.28804"},["b","6"],"¶Then he called for Solomon his son, and charged him to build an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"house"],"for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Israel."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.7","order":"02.14.022.28805"},["b","7"],"And David said to Solomon, My son, as for me, it was in my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"mind"],"to build an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"house"],"unto the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"my God:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.8","order":"02.14.022.28806"},["b","8"],"But the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came to me, saying, Thou hast shed blood abundantly, and hast made great wars: thou shalt not build an house unto my name, because thou hast shed much blood upon the earth in my sight."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.9","order":"02.14.022.28807"},["b","9"],"Behold, a son shall be born to thee, who shall be a man of rest; and I will give him",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"rest"],"from all his enemies round about: for his name shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"Solomon"],", and I will give peace and quietness unto Israel in his days."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.10","order":"02.14.022.28808"},["b","10"],"He shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"build"],"an house for my name; and he shall be my son, and I",["i","will be"],"his father; and I will establish the throne of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"kingdom"],"over Israel for ever."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.11","order":"02.14.022.28809"},["b","11"],"Now, my son, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"be with thee; and prosper thou, and build the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, as he hath said of thee."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.12","order":"02.14.022.28810"},["b","12"],"Only the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"give thee wisdom and understanding, and give thee charge concerning Israel, that thou mayest keep the law of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.13","order":"02.14.022.28811"},["b","13"],"Then shalt thou prosper, if thou takest heed to fulfil the statutes and judgments which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"charged Moses with concerning Israel: be strong, and of good",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"courage"],"; dread not, nor be dismayed."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.14","order":"02.14.022.28812"},["b","14"],"Now, behold, in my trouble I have prepared for the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"an hundred thousand",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"talents"],"of gold, and a thousand thousand talents of silver; and of brass and iron without weight; for it is in abundance: timber also and stone have I prepared; and thou mayest add thereto."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.15","order":"02.14.022.28813"},["b","15"],"Moreover",["i","there are"],"workmen with thee in abundance, hewers and workers of stone and timber, and all manner of cunning men for every manner of work."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.16","order":"02.14.022.28814"},["b","16"],"Of the gold, the silver, and the brass, and the iron,",["i","there is"],"no number. Arise",["i","therefore,"],"and be doing, and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"be with thee."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.17","order":"02.14.022.28815"},["b","17"],"¶David also commanded all the princes of Israel to help Solomon his son,",["i","saying,"]],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.18","order":"02.14.022.28816"},["b","18"],["i","Is"],"not the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God with you? and hath he",["i","not"],"given you rest on every side? for he hath given the inhabitants of the land into mine hand; and the land is subdued before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and before his people."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.19","order":"02.14.022.28817"},["b","19"],"Now set your heart and your soul to seek the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God; arise therefore, and build ye the sanctuary of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God, to bring the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"ark"],"of the covenant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and the holy vessels of God, into the house that is to be built to the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.1a","order":"02.14.022.28818"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/3.1"},"2 Chr. 3:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.1b","order":"02.14.022.28820"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/24.18"},"2 Sam. 24:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.2a","order":"02.14.022.28822"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/9.21"},"1 Kgs. 9:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.2b","order":"02.14.022.28824"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-land-of"},"TG Israel, Land of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.4a","order":"02.14.022.28826"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.6"},"1 Kgs. 5:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.5a","order":"02.14.022.28828"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/3.7"},"1 Kgs. 3:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/29.1"},"1 Chr. 29:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.6a","order":"02.14.022.28830"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temple"},"TG Temple"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.7a","order":"02.14.022.28832"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.3.3-5"},"2 Sam. 7:3 (3–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.7b","order":"02.14.022.28834"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/132.5.1-5"},"Ps. 132:5 (1–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.9a","order":"02.14.022.28836"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/4.24.24-25"},"1 Kgs. 4:24 (24–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.4"},"5:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.9b","order":"02.14.022.28838"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/12.24.24-25"},"2 Sam. 12:24 (24–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/1.13.11-14"},"1 Kgs. 1:13 (11–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.10a","order":"02.14.022.28840"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.12"},"1 Kgs. 6:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.10b","order":"02.14.022.28842"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/2.15"},"1 Kgs. 2:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.13a","order":"02.14.022.28844"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/courage"},"TG Courage"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.14a","order":"02.14.022.28846"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/29.4"},"1 Chr. 29:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.19a","order":"02.14.022.28848"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ark-of-the-covenant"},"TG Ark of the Covenant"],"."]]}
